snippet.title: Johnny Depp joins wife Amber Heard at TIFF premiere - Daily Mail
snippet.description:
As Johnny Depp and Dakota Johnson continue to promote their new movie Black Mass, the actors showed off rather contrasting looks on the red carpet on Monday. Johnson, 25, looked effortlessly stylish in a striped wrap dress and lace-up heels as she joined Depp, 52 at a press conference for the movie at the Toronto International Film Festival. The Fifty Shades Of Grey beauty wore her shoulder-length tresses in tousled waves and wore just a hint of make-up for a natural look.
